Additionally, the paper discusses the use of computational frameworks and algorithms, which could also place it in the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates its method on images, which could place it in the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
